INSERT INTO v2_job_completed AS cj
                    ( workspace_id
                    , id
                    , started_at
                    , duration_ms
                    , result
                    , result_columns
                    , canceled_by
                    , canceled_reason
                    , flow_status
                    , memory_peak
                    , status
                    )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, COALESCE($12::bigint, (EXTRACT('epoch' FROM (now())) - EXTRACT('epoch' FROM (COALESCE($3, now()))))*1000), $5, $13, $7, $8, $9,$11, CASE WHEN $6::BOOL THEN 'canceled'::job_status
                        WHEN $10::BOOL THEN 'skipped'::job_status
                        WHEN $4::BOOL THEN 'success'::job_status
                        ELSE 'failure'::job_status END)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET status = EXCLUDED.status, result = $5 RETURNING duration_ms AS "duration_ms!"
